history.content: Your application will definitely be considered, especially for the position of AI and tutor. However, it's highly unlikely you'll be appointed TA without substantial teaching experience if you haven't taken the class at all

I'm wondering if I can TA/lab assist for Data 8 without having taken the class. For reference, I have taken Data 100, CS189, EE126, CS186, CS170, all the CS lower divs, and engage in data science research. So I feel like I'd have a grasp of the course content. I'm just wondering if I would be considered for a position as a tutor/assistant/TA in Data 8 with these classes and w/o taking Data 8.
